| IC Number       | 7400   |
| Logic Family    | TTL    |
| Gate Type       | NAND   |
| Number of Gates | 4      |
| Inputs per Gate | 2      |
| Supply Voltage  | +5V    |
| Package Type    | DIP-14 |

